    Number: 54
Title: Love's Reasons
---
It’s not for nothing that I love you.
Others love my rosy complexion, but you love my gray hair.

It’s not for nothing that I long for you.
Others love my smile, but you love my tears.

It’s not for nothing that I wait for you.
Others love my vigor, but you love my death.
